# 1. Run the Login request first
# 2. Copy the token from response
# 3. Replace {{token}} variable above
# 4. Test protected endpoints

### Notes:
# - Default password for demo: "demo123"
# - Token expires in 24 hours (1440 minutes) in Development
# - Token expires in 60 minutes (default) in Production
# - Token contains: userId, email, roles (User, Admin)
